=== Climate action ===

Denmark's green house gas emissions per dollar of value produced has been for the most part unstable since 1990, seeing sudden growths and falls. Overall though, there has been a reduction in gas emissions per dollar value added to its market. It lags behind other Scandinavian countries such as [[Norway]] and [[Sweden]]. <ref>[[wikipedia:Denmark#Environment]]</ref>

